    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-broccoli-cheeze-pasta/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Cut your <strong>broccoli</strong> into small florets</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-broccoli-cheeze-pasta/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pasta</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for an initial 3 min</p><p>After an initial 3 min, add the <strong>broccoli florets</strong> to a pot for cook for a further 4-5 min, or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>broccoli</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-broccoli-cheeze-pasta/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your<strong> cheddar flavour block[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-broccoli-cheeze-pasta/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Add your<strong> creamy single oat</strong>,<strong> grated cheddar flavour block[s]</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> (not a mustard fan? Go easy!) and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened \u2013 this is your <strong>cheeze sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-broccoli-cheeze-pasta/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-broccoli-cheeze-pasta/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, stir in the<strong> drained spaghetti & broccoli</strong> and <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> through the cheeze sauce \u2013 this is your <strong>plant-based broccoli cheeze pasta</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-broccoli-cheeze-pasta/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>plant-based broccoli cheeze pasta </strong>and season with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Garnish with your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
